name: Dark FB Remake
description: A black Facebook theme for those who do not like the shiny white one.
additional_info: This is a remake from my old theme (Dark FB), it is still a work in progress therefore some components had not been styled yet, I'll be updating this theme but at the time I wanted to share it with you as is, hope you like it.
